# Frontend Environment Variables

Copy this file to `.env.local` in the `software/` directory.

```env
# API Server URL
REACT_APP_API_URL=http://localhost:4000
```

## For Production

Change to your actual backend URL:
```env
REACT_APP_API_URL=https://your-backend-domain.railway.app
```

This will be set automatically during Vercel deployment if you configure it in the project settings.
